<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Career Studio • TechMinds Academy</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    html { font-family: 'Inter', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 text-slate-800">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 pt-24 pb-16">
    <header class="mb-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">Career Studio</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Book Mentor Office Hours</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Get personalised feedback on your portfolio, resume, or interview preparation with TechMinds mentors.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">How it works</h2>
      <ol class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">1.</span> Choose a 30-minute slot that fits your schedule.</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">2.</span> Share the focus of your session (portfolio review, interview prep, etc.).</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">3.</span> Join the mentor on Google Meet at the scheduled time.</li>
      </ol>
      <a href="https://cal.com/techminds/mentor-office-hours" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-blue-700" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book a mentor session</a>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Resources to prepare</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-blue-700">
        <li><a href="https://techmindsacademy.org/blog/portfolio-checklist" class="hover:text-blue-800" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Portfolio checklist for tech roles →</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://techmindsacademy.org/blog/interview-questions" class="hover:text-blue-800" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Top behavioural interview questions →</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:career@techminds.academy" class="hover:text-blue-800">Email the career team →</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
